# PC Playground User Manual

**Author:** Michael Semar  
**Date:** 12/5/2023  
**Application Name:** PC Playground  
**Version:** 1.0

## Overview

Welcome to PC Playground, a user-friendly application designed to help you check the compatibility of components while building your computer. This user manual will guide you through the features and usage of the application.

